caption.p: Effect of CS-LO on LPS-induced cell viability, PGE 2, TNF- α, IL-1 β, and IL-6 in RAW 264.7 cells: (a) cell viability, (b) PGE 2 production, (c) TNF- α production, (d) IL-1 β production, and (e) IL-6 production. The data represent the means ± SD values from three independent experiments. ∗ P < 0.05, ∗∗ P < 0.01, and ∗∗∗ and P < 0.001 compared to the LPS-treated cells alone.
